		<title>04Illston - work in the area</title>
		<content> The farms provide the bulk of the work
 available in the area.  There is a    
 chicken breeding farm called Padley's 
 in Illston which employs 5 people.  At
 Thistley Close Cottages near to Three 
 Gates there is a small agricultural   
 trailer manufacturers which employs 4 
 people.  The farms themselves are     
 worked by the main farmer and perhaps 
 one or two labourers.  Modernisation  
 having made farming less labour       
 intensive than in past years.         
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
